<div class="jumbotron">
  <h2><%= gettext "Welcome to %{name}!", name: "File-Surrender" %></h2>
  <p class="lead">
    A place where you can keep you secret passwords secure in the cloud.<br/>
    The concept is simple: you sign in using your existing user account on Google, Facebook, VK, etc.<br/>
    When signed in for the first time, we ask you to specify your secret passphrase which will serve as the key<br/>
    for encrypting/decrypting your data.<br/>
    No part of your user ID or passphrase will be stored as plain text.<br/>
    So your data cannot be deciphered even by the database owner.
  </p>
</div>


